 Quilldart walked onto the bridge. "I gave the new girl her memory back. He 
walked over and handed him a disk. Galvatron put it into a slide poclet in 
his hip. "Very good Quilldart. Empath I want you and Quilldart to bring 
Nightshade on a routine scouting mission. We know barely anything of the 
tripred defenses. If our little espionage plot does not work....we'll need 
that information. You will be in charge so Quilldart follow her orders."

--part1_94.29876cc7.2a69a175_boundary
